name: AUTO DA FE - CORPUS HYPERCUBUS
description:
Autodafé (Spanish auto de fe, Portuguese auto de fé, from Latin actus fidei, "JUDGMENT ON FAITH") refers to the solemn, usually public pronouncement of the verdicts of the trials of the Spanish Inquisition or the Portuguese Inquisition.
